OL,6,FITV Border's Alice Neil takes a look
OL,7,Fat this year's count
OL,9,FThe annual Big Butterfly Count is back
OL,10,Fand organisers are encouraging more
OL,11,Fpeople than ever to take part as
OL,12,Fnumbers hit record lows.
OL,14,FButterfly numbers are currently the
OL,15,Flowest recorded in the 14-year history
OL,16,Fof Butterfly Conservation's Big
OL,17,FButterfly Count.
