OL,6,FLast year 4,824 butterflies were
OL,7,Fspotted in Cumbria. This year,
OL,8,Fparticipants are seeing just over half
OL,9,Fthe number of butterflies they were
OL,10,Fspotting at the same time in 2023.
OL,12,FApithanny Bourne from Butterfly
OL,13,FConservation said: "We are two weeks
OL,14,Finto Butterfly Conservation's big
OL,15,Fbutterfly count.
OL,17,F"We have noticed that the records of
OL,18,Fbutterflies coming in are much, much
OL,19,Flower than usual.
