OL,6,F"Butterflies are having a hard time
OL,7,Fanyway, and it makes them less
OL,8,Fresilient when we have a year with
OL,9,Freally poor weather."
OL,11,FThe low numbers are thought to be
OL,12,Fbecause of the wet and windy spring
OL,13,Fand a cold start to summer.
OL,15,FDr Dan Hoare, from Butterfly
OL,16,FConservation, said: "Butterflies need
OL,17,Fsome warm and dry conditions to be
OL,18,Fable to fly around and mate.
