OL,6,F"If the weather doesn't allow for this
OL,7,Fthere will be fewer opportunities to
OL,8,Fbreed, and the lack of butterflies now
OL,9,Fis likely the knock-on effect of our
OL,10,Fvery dreary spring and early summer."
OL,12,FEighty per cent of butterflies in the
OL,13,FUK have declined since the 1970s, the
OL,14,Fcharity warns that habitat loss,
OL,15,Fclimate change and pesticide use are
OL,16,Fthe main drivers of this decline.
